      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout with honest character? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great chance for someone who wants cheap, usable transport or a project to tidy up over time. It\u2019s being sold as-is and priced accordingly, with plenty of value for the right buyer. If you\u2019re after something straightforward, budget-friendly, and worth a look, send me a message.",
