      "description": "This car has the kind of presence you notice before you even turn the key\u2014a seasoned machine with real personality and a story in every panel. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who loves bringing life back into something with character, whether you want a budget-friendly driver, a hands-on project, or a distinctive ride with old-school soul. There\u2019s an undeniable charm here that newer cars just can\u2019t fake, and at this price, it\u2019s a chance to grab something memorable and make it your own.",
      "price": 5900.0,
