      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical choice for buyers seeking dependable value, a project opportunity, or an inexpensive second vehicle. A sensible pick for someone who wants honest utility without a big investment.",
